headline: Garmin receives 10th consecutive best supplier recognition from Embraer
summary: Garmin (NYSE: GRMN) today announced it received a Best Supplier of the Year award for the tenth consecutive year by Embraer at its annual Suppliers Conference which was held at Embraer's Eugênio de Melo facility April 14-15. Embraer, a leading aerospace manufacturer, recognized Garmin as the top supplier in the Electrical & Electronic Systems category for its G3000® Prodigy Touch flight deck systems in the Phenom 100EV and Phenom 300E.
